                                            <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2012/08/06/anti-status-quo-filmmakers-father-wounded-in-wisconsin-sikh-temple-shooting/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Anti-Status Quo Filmmaker&#8217;s Father Wounded in Wisconsin Sikh Temple Shooting">Anti-Status Quo Filmmaker&#8217;s Father Wounded in Wisconsin Sikh Temple Shooting</a></h2>
                <?php// rtp_hook_end_post_title(); ?>

                
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-top"><span class="author"><a class="fn" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/author/mkriegs/" title="Posts by Michael Krieger">Michael Krieger</a></span> <span class="rtp-meta-separator">|</span> Posted <time class="published" datetime="2012-08-06T09:42:07+00:00">Monday Aug 6, 2012</time> at 9:42 am         <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2012/08/06/anti-status-quo-filmmakers-father-wounded-in-wisconsin-sikh-temple-shooting/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Anti-Status Quo Filmmaker&#8217;s Father Wounded in Wisconsin Sikh Temple Shooting"><span>2</span> Comments</a></span>
            </div><!-- .post-meta -->            </header><!-- .post-title -->

            <div class="post-content">
                                

                
                <p>The Wisconsin shooting tragedy took a huge turn for me ever since I heard that one of the seriously wounded is Satwant Singh Kaleka, father of Amardeep Kaleka, who is intimately involved in the creation of the movie Sirius, a film that from what I can tell may expose information that TPTB do not want to the broader public to see.  Quite the coincidence in my opinion and no matter what your biases are, I implore you to keep an open mind.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.jsonline.com/news/crime/reports-of-people-shot-at-sikh-temple-in-oak-creek-qc6cgc0-165059506.html?page=1#!page=1&amp;pageSize=10&amp;sort=newestfirst">Here is an article</a> on the shooting where Amardeep Kaleka has his head in his hands in a photo at the top.</p>
<p>Here is a link to the <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lp9aOb04e20&amp;feature=player_embedded#!">trailer for the movie Sirius</a>, in which Amardeep makes several appearances.</p>
<p>Furthermore, here is Amardeep saying there were multiple shooters involved.</p>
<p><span class='embed-youtube' style='text-align:center; display: block;'><iframe class='youtube-player' type='text/html' width='620' height='379' src='http://www.youtube.com/embed/1qSt6LoXQ6A?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent' frameborder='0'></iframe></span><br />
My deepest thoughts and prayers go out to Amardeep, his father and all the others affected by this horrific tragedy.</p>
<p>In Truth, Compassion, Love and Liberty,<br />
Mike</p>
