            <header class="post-header ">
                
                                            <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2012/07/22/inaugural-interview-with-kerry-lutz-july-2012/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Inaugural Interview with Kerry Lutz &#8211; July 2012">Inaugural Interview with Kerry Lutz &#8211; July 2012</a></h2>
                <?php// rtp_hook_end_post_title(); ?>

                
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-top"><span class="author"><a class="fn" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/author/mkriegs/" title="Posts by Michael Krieger">Michael Krieger</a></span> <span class="rtp-meta-separator">|</span> Posted <time class="published" datetime="2012-07-22T16:29:32+00:00">Sunday Jul 22, 2012</time> at 4:29 pm         <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2012/07/22/inaugural-interview-with-kerry-lutz-july-2012/#respond" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Inaugural Interview with Kerry Lutz &#8211; July 2012">Leave a comment</a></span>
            </div><!-- .post-meta -->            </header><!-- .post-title -->

            <div class="post-content">
                                

                
                <p>Early last week, I had the great pleasure to record my first podcast with Kerry Lutz of the <a href="http://financialsurvivalnetwork.com/">Financial Survival Network</a>.  I was fortunate enough to meet Kerry recently for the first time at Freedom Fest in Las Vegas, and we spent what seemed like hours talking about our respective paths in life and how we can defeat the criminals running and enslaving America and the world today.  We discuss everything from the coming attempts at a &#8220;cashless society,&#8221; to NSA Whistleblowers and what TPTB next move might be.</p>
<p>Please have a listen <a href="http://ec.libsyn.com/p/e/f/1/ef1a147213cdfbfc/Michael_Krieger_07-18-2012.mp3?d13a76d516d9dec20c3d276ce028ed5089ab1ce3dae902ea1d01cc853ed8ce5a46ec&amp;c_id=4718133">here</a>!</p>
